LaTeX Palettes\
\pard\tx560\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\qj

\fs22 \cf0 \ulnone \
Since version 1.14.0, LaTeXiT handles LaTeX palettes as plugins. Built-in palettes are inside the application, but additional palettes can be installed inside the Library folders, in a sub-folder Application Support/LaTeXiT/Palettes.\
Examples :\
/Library/Application Support/LaTeXiT/Palettes\
/Users/[your name]/Library/Application Support/LaTeXiT/Palettes\
/Network/Library/Application Support/LaTeXiT/Palettes\
\
A palette is a folder with the following structure:\
name.latexpalette\
     |_Info.plist\
     |_Resources\
          |_English.lproj
\fs26 \ul \

\fs22 \ulnone                |_Localizable.strings\
          |_French.lproj\
               |_Localizable.strings\
          |...image files...\
\
